org.beanfabrics.meta

Class PathElementInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.beanfabrics.meta.PathElementInfo

  • public class PathElementInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    The PathElementInfo represents the meta data for a Path element relative to a concrete root TypeInfo. With a PathElementInfo you can navigate from a path element to it's root element, and to its children.
    Author:
    Michael Karneim
